      "most_relevant": [
        {
          "username": "Matthew Inge",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "101469120635964673748",
          "user_review_count": 5,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo4xWpztWjA4NJCKbhNQwIPICdlrktc-Kl_T7L85xbSroWnGpc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Those reviews leaving one star have been proven to be fake reviews blackmailing the company to pay them to take away the negative reviews ... This was reported on the local 11 pm news.\n\nI live in the same building that Danny's II is located.  Sevice is always excellent.  Danny is great, as all the pharmacists that work there.  Danny is all for the neighborhood and is grateful for all the neigbors who stop in.  He knows most by name.  The staff is always friendly, helpful and very competent. They even notify me that my prescription is due before I even notice.  And it is ready for me to pickup.  They also deliver.  I also get my flu and COVID shots there.  No hassle ... no stadning in line for hours like I used to do at CVS before Danny's opened here.  Even there were times I needed unusual medicine that most pharmacies don't have in stock, he found what I needed and I was able to pick it up the next day.  If you're looking for a excellent pharmacy, that is friendly and will take care of you ... stop by Danny's II ... make up your own mind and see my review is the truth.  Be healthy",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21oM2NrRlFaQzAxWlhSaVpsTlNaMVZXZUU1a1gwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x293c40234ac13bb4!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmh3ckFQZC01ZXRiZlNSZ1VWeE5kX0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
