          "contributor_id": "108589969342187943524",
          "user_review_count": 3,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRsxERg4mch7FaUGQ2V-sW3jhXu9dUeS_UxDM8iVLlscMC1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "Both Danny and Yuri, the pharmacists take exceptional care of my family. They go above and beyond. Phones are answered promptly, deliveries are made quickly and efficiently, and everyone is polite and helpful. I feel very fortunate to have such a reliable pharmacy in my neighborhood. I know I can count on them.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aM2NEZFBaVFZ0YTJ4bk9HVnJPSGxzTWxwQmNYYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x293c40234ac13bb4!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmZ3cDdPZTVta2xnOGVrOHlsMlpBcXc%7C%7C?hl=en",
