          "description": "Such a breath of fresh air !! Preparing and picking up  prescriptions are fastest I\u2019ve ever experienced. Zero wait times when you call and don\u2019t have to go through lengthy automated systems. Time saving and efficient to the max. They are the best! Highly recommend.",
