          "description": "Danny was unbelievably helpful to me & my family during holiday peak flu season!  He had xoflu in stock when all the mass pharmacies were out. This is my new go to pharmacy\u2014highly recommend for personal touch and hard to find prescriptions. Thank you Danny for being such a delight!",
